<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_322_r1l1">Hanſen Gevvolff <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dege<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>Vicʒt<ex>um</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
