<ab>Hansen Gewolff <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Dege<ex>m</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>viczt<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        czü <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her vicztüm, es hat unser
                                <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r,</expan> herczog Johans,
                            <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Michelsperg<ex>er</ex></expan> einen tag gemachet, gen Sulczbach <app><note><q type="date">auf
                            den nehsten <expan>mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>19.08.1411</note></app> czü
                            <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> tag czeit do cze sein. Nu
                                <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> czemal
                            <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir auf den
                                <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag also dahin kumen und bey den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein wöllet und in beygestendig
                                <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Und getrawen ew
                                <expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir uns das nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagen</expan> wöllet. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>pc<ex>ionis</ex></expan> Marie.</ab>
</div>
